reviewText: Great video and the service was fantastic from start to finish.
My autistic son loves videos.  He was thrilled to get this.  We received it in plenty of time for xmas.

I loved this tape. My niece is four years old, and we were going on a road trip... Well, anyone who has kids would know how brutal that is!
This kept her entertained and laughing throughout the whole thing... she even made me play it twice! It was a blast, and kept her tied over for the last hour or so of the trip.
I also loved it, not just my niece. It was really cute and fun, and had all these bright colors! It wad perfect.
